                "if the illuminance sensor is dark",
                "when the illuminance sensor becomes dark",
                "if the illuminance sensor becomes dark",
                "when the illuminance sensor turns dark",
                "if the illuminance sensor turns dark",
                "when the illuminance sensor gets dark",
                "if the illuminance sensor gets dark"]];

